00:08:46.125 --> 00:08:46.975
Astaga!

00:08:47.745 --> 00:08:48.545
Warna abu-abu.

00:08:48.955 --> 00:08:50.115
Tubuh yang bagus!

00:08:50.515 --> 00:08:51.505
Ban bersinar.

00:08:51.735 --> 00:08:53.595
Ketika itu datang
ke arahku dari jauh...

