Sampai jumpa besok.

00:09:21.018 --> 00:09:21.818
Astaga!

00:09:23.108 --> 00:09:24.558
Saya sangat menyukainya.

00:09:28.758 --> 00:09:29.758
Selamat tinggal!

00:09:30.500 --> 00:09:31.695
Ayo, sayangku.

00:09:57.910 --> 00:09:58.710
Tertawa!

00:09:59.379 --> 00:10:01.223
Tertawalah sebanyak yang kamu mau.
Anda akan mati tertawa.

00:10:01.304 --> 00:10:02.304
Tunggu sebentar.

